window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>FROM THE ICE.... </p> <p>A mammoth, flash frozen in solid ice 10,000 years ago is brought to the surface by a team of scientists. An act of sabotage frees the giant from its icy tomb and reveals the secret held inside. </p> <p>OUT OF THE MAMMOTH.... </p> <p>The body of an ancient woman, cloaked in furs, slides out of the mammoth's belly. But it is not the woman that holds the team's attention - it is the object she is clutching: a device created by an advanced civilization. </p> <p>THE HUNT IS ON.... </p> <p>The device is accidentally activated, summoning forces who seek its destruction. It is the key to mankind's salvation and freedom from the sinister force hiding behind the curtain, pulling the strings, and leading humanity towards destruction. </p>"; 
